  "body": "[Docs](https://www.npmjs.com/package/web3-provider-engine) indicate that the web3-provider-engine package which hdwallet-provider depends on is no longer actively maintained, in favor of [json-rpc-engine](https://www.npmjs.com/package/json-rpc-engine) and [eth-json-rpc-middleware](https://www.npmjs.com/package/eth-json-rpc-middleware).  This leads to issues like long delays in updating dependencies for security issues that bubble through to the hdwallet-provider package.  Truffle's hdwallet-provider package should update which package it depends on to a more actively maintained package.\r\n",
